==============================================================================
c2.patch.sharesettingcopy
==============================================================================



Installation
------------

Install c2.patch.sharesettingcopy by adding it to your buildout::

   [buildout]

    ...

    eggs =
        c2.patch.sharesettingcopy


and then running "bin/buildout"
